summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6318 for the improvement of the alley in Block 14, Replat of Blocks 1, 2, 6, 7, 13, 14 & 23, D.T. Denny's North Seattle, being the alley between 1st Ave. West and 2nd Ave. West from West Mercer Street to West Republican Street; by paving, etc.; under Ordinance No. 93881, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
